<div class="postdate">December 22, 2025</div>
<div class="posts">
<ul><li>
UC San Diego Today published a nice article today, "UC San Diego is Strengthening U.S. Semiconductor Innovation and Workforce Development", about several ongoing efforts in our lab. The article is <a href="https://today.ucsd.edu/story/uc-san-diego-is-strengthening-u.s-semiconductor-innovation-and-workforce-development">HERE</a> [cached <a href="NEWS25/20251022_UCSanDiegoStrengtheningUSSemiconductorInnovationAndWorkforceDevelopment.pdf">.pdf of the article</a>].
