<div class="posts">
<ul><li>
Prof. Kahng gave a workshop talk today on "How We Will Make an Automated Digital IC Designer". His slides are <a href="./NEWS25/Kahng-AutomatedDigitalICDesigner-20251020-v3a-FINAL-WITHNOTES-clean.pptx">HERE</a> (.pptx with speaker notes, plus <a href="./NEWS25/Kahng-AutomatedDigitalICDesigner-20251020-v3a-FINAL-WITHNOTES-clean.pdf">.pdf</a>). Please also see (<a href="./NEWS25/AmurGhose-Poster-v2.pptx">.pptx</a>, <a href="./NEWS25/AmurGhose-Poster-v2.pdf">.pdf</a>) of the accompanying poster presented by Amur Ghose.
</li>
</ul>
</div>

