<ul><li>
We are happy to note the opening of our GitHub repo for the <a href="https://github.com/ABKGroup/ISPD26-Contest">ISPD26 Contest</a> on Post-Placement Buffering and Sizing. Kudos to Sayak Kundu, Yiting Liu and Davit Markarian, as well as to our co-organizers Seonghyeon Park and Zhiang Wang, for all their efforts. And, many thanks to the NSF Chipshub, NVIDIA, and the ISPD committee for their support. We look forward to an exciting contest!
</li>
</ul>
